content: तुंज् {c1c} <ab>P.</ab> (तुंजति) <ab>Ved.</ab> {@--1@} To reach, extend, convey. {@--2@} To kill, hurt. {@--3@} To guard, protect. {@--4@} To clothe. {@--5@} To live. {@--6@} To strike, hit. {@--7@} To push. {@--8@} To emit, send forth. {@--9@} To incite, instigate, urge onwards. {@--10@} To give.
